1. Juče sam *pogledala* novu epizodu omiljene serije. (Yesterday, I watched the new episode of my favorite TV show.)
2. Kada *pogledaš* kroz ovaj prozor, vidiš predivan zalazak sunca. (When you look through this window, you can see a beautiful sunset.)
3. Nakon što je *pogledala* poruku, odmah mi je odgovorila. (After she saw the message, she replied to me immediately.)
4. *Pogledaj* malo bolje, možda ćeš uočiti nešto novo. (Look a little closer, maybe you'll notice something new.)
5. Ona je bila *pogledana* od strane mnogih ljudi zbog svog neobičnog izgleda. (She was looked at by many people because of her unusual appearance.)
6. Kada bih *pogledala* unapred, nikada ne bih smela da krenem na ovaj put. (If I looked ahead, I would never have dared to go on this journey.)
7. *Pogledajte* samo koliko se grad promenio u poslednjih deset godina! (Just look at how much the city has changed in the last ten years!)
8. Kada sam *pogledala* u ogledalo, primetila sam da mi kosa izgleda drugačije. (When I looked in the mirror, I noticed that my hair looked different.)
9. Naša kuća se *pogleda* na prelepu šumu. (Our house overlooks a beautiful forest.)